Title: [Hypertrophic osteoarthropathy of the child. One case cured by antibiotherapy (author's transl)].
Abstract: Hypertrophic osteoarthropathy in a child is reported. It is caused by intrathoracic suppuration secondary to costal osteomyelitis. After antibiotherapy complete resolution of arthropathy, clubbing and periostitis is obtained. The literature is reviewed.
