Title: Volar wrist ganglia cured by carpal tunnel decompression.
Abstract: Three patients are described, each of whom had both carpal tunnel syndrome and a volar wrist ganglion. Carpal tunnel decompression caused resolution of the ganglion. This suggests that both disorders may be caused by the same pressure phenomenon.
